 have an angle of 25deg</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\"><span class=\"token variable\">$direction</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> -125deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Spread on 120px</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\"><span class=\"token variable\">$length</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 120px<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// From this color</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\"><span class=\"token variable\">$color</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #8e44ad<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// To transparent</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\"><span class=\"token variable\">$fade</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// With only 10 shadows</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\"><span class=\"token variable\">$shadow-count</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://dab1nmslvvntp.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/1421924369ECeMqZF.png\" alt=\"example 3\"></p>\n<p>最后可以去看看<a href=\"(http://codepen.io/SitePoint/pen/bNWXdQ)\">这个pen</a>。</p>\n<h2 id=\"参考文章\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0\" aria-label=\"参考文章 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1